org.flexiblepower.efi.util

Class TimerUpdate

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.flexiblepower.efi.util.TimerUpdate

  • public class TimerUpdate
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains up to date information about the state of the timers. A class sends updates of the timers that have a new finishedAt time. Timers that are not mentioned are assumed to have the same finishedAt time is the most recent TimerUpdate.
